  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 2,
  "lyrics": "I'm here for you. I was born for you. I'm here for you. I was born for you. I wake up, I shake off the new. The old day doesn't make me blue, no. I'm here for you. What are we gonna do today? My master, my owner, tell me the way. Oh, I know it hurts sometimes. The weird noises that come out of your mouth. I know it hurts you sometimes. I'm not trying to say that I know, but I'm here for you, no matter which way you roll. I encompass love as a bar, cause I tell you my thoughts, can't you hear? Cause you always got me. I was born for you. I love you. That's true. And sometimes I may see a little faction or movement and run past what your voice told me to do. But just know I'm just trying for you. To show you love, cause I think you need it. I'm trying to show you that it's about being happy where I can tell and be alright. Thank you for coming into my life, dude. I know I'll go away one day. You probably saved it. You can make that the best day of me, when you say my job's complete. Cause the world and all of that energy sent me to you. I'm here for you. Yours forever. I just wanna be loved too. I'm here for you. And all the rabbits and all the pesky little farmers that I need to catch will never take priority over you. My human, my man, you're the best thing that happened to me to give me purpose so I can finally see that I love every second, every moment that was made for you and me. I love you, Basie. You're the best dog in the world, dude. You are, dude.",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 14.739999771118164,
      "text": "I'm here for you. I was born for you. I'm here for you. I was born for you.",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 23.639999389648438,
      "text": "I wake up, I shake off the new. The old day doesn't make me blue, no.",
      "start": 16.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 34.459999084472656,
      "text": "I'm here for you. What are we gonna do today? My master, my owner, tell me the way.",
      "start": 23.639999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 48.720001220703125,
      "text": "Oh, I know it hurts sometimes. The weird noises that come out of your mouth. I know it hurts you sometimes.",
      "start": 37.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 57.13999938964844,
      "text": "I'm not trying to say that I know, but I'm here for you, no matter which way you roll.",
      "start": 48.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 64.94000244140625,
      "text": "I encompass love as a bar, cause I tell you my thoughts, can't you hear?",
      "start": 58.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 74.36000061035156,
      "text": "Cause you always got me. I was born for you. I love you. That's true.",
      "start": 64.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 87.33999633789062,
      "text": "And sometimes I may see a little faction or movement and run past what your voice told me to do.",
      "start": 79.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 96.5199966430664,
      "text": "But just know I'm just trying for you. To show you love, cause I think you need it.",
      "start": 87.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 105.0199966430664,
      "text": "I'm trying to show you that it's about being happy where I can tell and be alright.",
      "start": 97
    },
    {
      "end": 112.55999755859375,
      "text": "Thank you for coming into my life, dude. I know I'll go away one day.",
      "start": 105.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 114.83999633789062,
      "text": "You probably saved it.",
      "start": 112.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 123.23999786376953,
      "text": "You can make that the best day of me, when you say my job's complete.",
      "start": 115.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 133.25999450683594,
      "text": "Cause the world and all of that energy sent me to you. I'm here for you.",
      "start": 124.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 134.72000122070312,
      "text": "Yours forever.",
      "start": 133.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 144.02000427246094,
      "text": "I just wanna be loved too. I'm here for you.",
      "start": 134.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 158.94000244140625,
      "text": "And all the rabbits and all the pesky little farmers that I need to catch will never take priority over you.",
      "start": 146.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 169,
      "text": "My human, my man, you're the best thing that happened to me to give me purpose so I can finally see",
      "start": 159.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 176,
      "text": "that I love every second, every moment that was made for you and me.",
      "start": 169.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 182.55999755859375,
      "text": "I love you, Basie. You're the best dog in the world, dude. You are, dude.",
      "start": 176.36000061035156
    }
  ],
